1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:34,940
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

3
00:01:46,009 --> 00:01:48,080
[Episode 10]

4
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,320
Physician Li,

5
00:01:52,110 --> 00:01:54,830
I've been thinking about a small question.

6
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:59,370
Why don't you reveal your face?

7
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,680
Master Bai.

8
00:02:07,430 --> 00:02:08,470
Here's the thing.

9
00:02:09,020 --> 00:02:12,020
I'm just a physician who wanders in the martial arts world.

10
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:13,350
I'm rootless.

11
00:02:13,660 --> 00:02:16,410
It's also my duty to cure people and save people's lives.

12
00:02:16,410 --> 00:02:17,090
Besides,

13
00:02:17,660 --> 00:02:18,990
when I cure good people,

14
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:20,759
bad people want to kill me.

15
00:02:20,810 --> 00:02:22,090
When I cure bad people,

16
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:23,890
good people are not happy.

17
00:02:24,070 --> 00:02:26,540
There are so many people in the Sword-Appreciation Ceremony.

18
00:02:26,540 --> 00:02:28,420
There are also many enemies.

19
00:02:28,730 --> 00:02:29,990
It's not too much for me

20
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:31,790
to wear this mask, right?

21
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:34,560
Physician Li.

22
00:02:35,660 --> 00:02:36,540
But why

23
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:39,720
do I seem to have seen you somewhere before?

24
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:43,770
You've seen me before?

25
00:02:43,770 --> 00:02:44,300
Yes.

26
00:02:46,730 --> 00:02:47,740
Could it be

27
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,329
that you've seen my elder brother before?

28
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:52,560
Your elder brother?

29
00:02:54,260 --> 00:02:56,790
Have you really seen my elder brother before?

30
00:02:57,980 --> 00:02:59,240
I'm sorry, Master Yun.

31
00:03:00,250 --> 00:03:00,850
Yes.

32
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:04,670
I do have a twin brother.

33
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:06,060
My mother named us

34
00:03:06,410 --> 00:03:07,450
Li Lianpeng

35
00:03:07,610 --> 00:03:09,150
and Li Lianhua respectively.

36
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:11,260
-Li Lianpeng.
-Lianpeng is my elder brother.

37
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:13,050
I'm the younger brother.

38
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:15,460
We were born in a poor family.

39
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:19,960
Soon after my brother was born,

40
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:22,700
he was taken away by an old man

41
00:03:23,370 --> 00:03:24,430
as his adopted son.

42
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:28,230
Since then, I've never seen him again.

43
00:03:29,060 --> 00:03:30,110
But I also heard

44
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:33,550
that my brother is quite awesome.

45
00:03:34,210 --> 00:03:35,300
So in this world,

46
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:38,310
there is a person who resembles me.

47
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:42,780
Li Lianpeng?

48
00:03:42,900 --> 00:03:45,020
It's true. I never lie.

49
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,270
Physician Li.

50
00:03:52,770 --> 00:03:53,920
Your family is poor,

51
00:03:54,540 --> 00:03:57,210
but the Lotus Tower has a unique structure

52
00:03:57,300 --> 00:03:58,540
and shows exquisite craftsmanship.

53
00:03:58,540 --> 00:03:59,400
It's valuable.

54
00:04:00,030 --> 00:04:01,160
Where did you get it?

55
00:04:05,990 --> 00:04:08,050
A few years ago, I saw a big shabby boat

56
00:04:08,170 --> 00:04:10,130
floating on the sea.

57
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,570
No one had interest in it.

58
00:04:13,070 --> 00:04:15,130
So I picked up the wood

59
00:04:15,670 --> 00:04:17,310
and made it into a Lotus Tower.

60
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:19,790
You can ask the fishermen about it by the sea.

61
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:21,430
I didn't steal it.

62
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:27,370
Physician Li, what are you talking about?

63
00:04:27,649 --> 00:04:29,970
Biqiu just asked casually.

64
00:04:32,829 --> 00:04:33,490
Pingchuan.

65
00:04:36,370 --> 00:04:37,700
I was reckless just now.

66
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,550
I guess

67
00:04:39,890 --> 00:04:42,100
you haven't eaten anything since last night.

68
00:04:42,100 --> 00:04:43,480
This is the peanut porridge

69
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:46,090
I specially asked someone to buy from Zuijiang Restaurant.

70
00:04:46,090 --> 00:04:46,890
Physician Li.

71
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:47,510
Try it.

72
00:04:49,650 --> 00:04:50,909
Thank you, Master Yun.

73
00:04:51,490 --> 00:04:52,750
Sir, put it here.

74
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:53,909
I'll drink it later.

75
00:04:56,420 --> 00:04:58,280
If the peanut porridge gets cold,

76
00:04:58,780 --> 00:05:00,760
then my kindness is for nothing.

77
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:02,710
Drink it while it's hot.

78
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:08,180
Thank you.

79
00:05:09,740 --> 00:05:10,610
It smells good.

80
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,750
It looks good.

81
00:05:19,330 --> 00:05:21,110
Why are there peanuts in the porridge?

82
00:05:21,110 --> 00:05:22,170
Why can't there be?

83
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:24,190
Xiangyi has an allergy to peanuts.

84
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:25,730
This...

85
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:29,440
I have an allergic reaction again.

86
00:05:39,850 --> 00:05:42,190
Since you've been poisoned with the deadliest poison,

87
00:05:42,190 --> 00:05:45,010
no poison can harm you anymore.

88
00:05:46,530 --> 00:05:47,330
Physician Li.

89
00:05:47,850 --> 00:05:49,110
You still need to rest.

90
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:50,830
We won't disturb you then.

91
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:51,740
I've had enough porridge.

92
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:52,340
Thank you.

93
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:53,960
I won't see you off.

94
00:05:55,710 --> 00:05:56,240
Let's go.

95
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:07,110
Li Lianhua.

96
00:06:10,659 --> 00:06:14,550
Someone poisoned his friend who he respected most

97
00:06:15,820 --> 00:06:17,990
for a woman

98
00:06:18,700 --> 00:06:21,700
and caused his friend to fall into the East Sea and die.

99
00:06:21,850 --> 00:06:22,620
Do you think

100
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:25,860
this person deserves to die?

101
00:06:27,990 --> 00:06:29,870
Yes. He indeed deserves to die.

102
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:35,440
Did this person have intention to kill his friend?

103
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:38,700
That woman said

104
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:43,450
she didn't want Li Xiangyi to appear in the East Seaside.

105
00:06:43,670 --> 00:06:46,530
She didn't allow Di Feisheng to be killed by others.

106
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:49,980
But Sect Leader's martial art skills are unpredictable.

107
00:06:49,980 --> 00:06:52,490
If I hadn't poisoned him with the deadliest poison,

108
00:06:52,490 --> 00:06:54,090
I couldn't have stopped him.

109
00:06:54,770 --> 00:06:57,780
I thought I only needed to stop him for a while.

110
00:06:59,140 --> 00:07:00,650
I had the antidote anyway.

111
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:03,030
I thought it didn't matter.

112
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:05,080
But things weren't like that.

113
00:07:06,060 --> 00:07:07,440
The antidote is fake.

114
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:12,800
All the things happened because I was too stupid.

115
00:07:14,490 --> 00:07:16,290
Even if I didn't want to kill him,

116
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:19,840
I did kill him.

117
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:23,280
If you were Sect Leader,

118
00:07:24,570 --> 00:07:26,570
you would hate me to the core, right?

119
00:07:27,260 --> 00:07:28,520
If I were him,

120
00:07:29,860 --> 00:07:31,460
I would definitely hate you.

121
00:07:34,300 --> 00:07:35,360
But think about it.

122
00:07:35,610 --> 00:07:37,120
You said he has died.

123
00:07:37,780 --> 00:07:40,170
Why would the dead hate you?

124
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:41,740
Besides,

125
00:07:42,260 --> 00:07:44,870
all grudges are gone.

126
00:07:45,610 --> 00:07:47,110
They've become the past.

127
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,650
I think you should forget it.

128
00:07:52,590 --> 00:07:54,050
Should I really forget it?

129
00:07:57,060 --> 00:07:57,590
How is it?

130
00:07:58,630 --> 00:07:59,590
We've tested it.

131
00:07:59,790 --> 00:08:00,870
He's not him at all.

132
00:08:08,860 --> 00:08:11,690
He's really not him.

133
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,370
Mr. Li.

134
00:08:20,180 --> 00:08:20,730
Ms. Qiao.

135
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:28,970
Last time, you asked me to investigate the whereabouts of Shi Hun.

136
00:08:28,970 --> 00:08:30,120
I found some clues.

137
00:08:30,370 --> 00:08:32,100
[To Qiao Wanmian. May 28, the year of Renyin.]

138
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:32,800
When we let him go ten years ago,

139
00:08:33,070 --> 00:08:34,820
he wrote a letter to thank us.

140
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:37,990
It was sent from Cailian Manor in Xueyu Town.

141
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:40,600
But it happened ten years ago.

142
00:08:41,020 --> 00:08:42,400
There is a sea of faces in the world.

143
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:44,590
It's not easy to get some clues.

144
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:46,030
Thank you, Ms. Qiao.

145
00:08:46,220 --> 00:08:47,549
You're welcome, Mr. Li.

146
00:08:48,220 --> 00:08:51,230
Actually, I'm here today also for another thing.

147
00:08:51,990 --> 00:08:52,919
Say it, Ms. Qiao.

148
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,000
The sachet...

149
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,880
You reminded me.

150
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:06,940
Mr. Xiao took you away in a hurry yesterday.

151
00:09:06,940 --> 00:09:08,100
I kept it.

152
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:10,750
It belonged to your deceased friend.

153
00:09:10,850 --> 00:09:12,250
I should return it to you.

154
00:09:18,820 --> 00:09:19,350
Ms. Qiao.

155
00:09:24,700 --> 00:09:28,860
I made this sachet for him.

156
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,370
It's been ten years.

157
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:34,250
I've held out hope

158
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,650
for ten years.

159
00:09:47,180 --> 00:09:49,180
Although I thought about it before,

160
00:09:51,700 --> 00:09:53,560
the fact that he doesn't come back

161
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:55,490
is the answer.

162
00:10:01,850 --> 00:10:02,530
Although

163
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:07,630
I'm mentally prepared,

164
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,590
when

165
00:10:10,890 --> 00:10:12,730
I heard he is dead,

166
00:10:13,690 --> 00:10:14,380
I still...

167
00:10:17,780 --> 00:10:18,700
I still...

168
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,330
Ms. Qiao.

169
00:10:21,130 --> 00:10:22,590
He's already passed away.

170
00:10:23,410 --> 00:10:26,080
Don't be too sad.

171
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:31,500
Mr. Li.

172
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:35,640
I...

173
00:10:42,790 --> 00:10:44,360
I once had

174
00:10:47,570 --> 00:10:49,520
some ridiculous thoughts.

175
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:02,280
It was just because I couldn't accept the reality.

176
00:11:02,530 --> 00:11:03,770
I deceived myself.

177
00:11:04,780 --> 00:11:05,470
Now,

178
00:11:06,940 --> 00:11:08,200
I should clear my mind.

179
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:13,630
This is his personal item.

180
00:11:17,940 --> 00:11:19,600
It's good to let it go with him.

181
00:11:32,770 --> 00:11:37,110
The ten-year wait has ended.

182
00:11:52,350 --> 00:11:54,210
Since he's your deceased friend,

183
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:55,660
let him stay in the story.

184
00:11:57,350 --> 00:12:00,390
Ms. Qiao, you should move on without worries.

185
00:12:02,380 --> 00:12:03,020
Mr. Li.

186
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,510
Thank you.

187
00:12:18,930 --> 00:12:19,480
Ms. Qiao.

188
00:12:25,250 --> 00:12:26,980
Why did Ms. Qiao also come here?

189
00:12:29,570 --> 00:12:30,570
Let me remind you.

190
00:12:30,820 --> 00:12:32,740
Ms. Qiao is already spoken for.

191
00:12:32,970 --> 00:12:34,430
Don't have designs on her.

192
00:12:36,540 --> 00:12:38,110
I heard from the little monks in the courtyard

193
00:12:38,110 --> 00:12:41,440
that all the masters of the Baichuan Court came here before.

194
00:12:42,460 --> 00:12:43,990
You didn't come at that time.

195
00:12:43,990 --> 00:12:44,990
Do you know

196
00:12:45,930 --> 00:12:47,390
what Master Ji brought me?

197
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:49,440
Shaoshi Sword.

198
00:12:49,780 --> 00:12:50,640
Shaoshi Sword?

199
00:12:51,830 --> 00:12:52,760
Did you touch it?

200
00:12:52,900 --> 00:12:53,890
Of course.

201
00:12:54,650 --> 00:12:55,540
To be honest,

202
00:12:56,450 --> 00:12:58,110
I saved Ms. Qiao in the tunnel.

203
00:12:58,860 --> 00:12:59,920
In order to thank me,

204
00:12:59,920 --> 00:13:01,070
they let me have a look

205
00:13:01,070 --> 00:13:02,310
and touch it.

206
00:13:02,890 --> 00:13:03,750
Let me tell you.

207
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,530
This sword is really heavy.

208
00:13:05,710 --> 00:13:06,960
My hand hurt when I touched it.

209
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,580
I couldn't lift it immediately.

210
00:13:08,580 --> 00:13:10,440
You're so lucky.

211
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:11,870
I can't even touch it.

212
00:13:13,410 --> 00:13:13,900
Look.

213
00:13:14,210 --> 00:13:15,510
My hand became callused after I touched it.

214
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:16,200
Cut it out.

215
00:13:16,950 --> 00:13:17,830
How rude of you!

216
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:19,500
You've taken your medicine?

217
00:13:19,910 --> 00:13:21,040
I've told Bhante Wuliao.

218
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:22,440
He'll check on you later.

219
00:13:24,060 --> 00:13:24,650
Thanks.

220
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:40,220
How long do you think your life

221
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:41,880
will let you suffer like this?

222
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:43,560
I've warned you many times.

223
00:13:44,190 --> 00:13:46,590
You have the unique Yangzhouman.

224
00:13:46,980 --> 00:13:47,820
That's why you still have

225
00:13:47,820 --> 00:13:50,650
ten percent of the internal power which can protect your heart.

226
00:13:50,650 --> 00:13:53,430
Every time you use it, the effect of the poison accelerates.

227
00:13:53,430 --> 00:13:54,910
Why don't you listen?

228
00:13:55,770 --> 00:13:58,920
Bicha Poison will affect your brain.

229
00:13:59,210 --> 00:14:00,470
You're a smart person.

230
00:14:00,780 --> 00:14:03,040
If you suddenly become crazy and stupid,

231
00:14:03,790 --> 00:14:05,940
I... I won't be used to it.

232
00:14:06,770 --> 00:14:08,080
You have to get used to it.

233
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,220
Old Monk, stop talking.

234
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:10,550
If you continue to talk,

235
00:14:10,910 --> 00:14:11,820
I will have a headache

236
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:13,350
and won't hear you clearly.

237
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,480
Don't interrupt.

238
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:17,960
If you continue to use Genuine Qi at will,

239
00:14:18,180 --> 00:14:20,780
I'm afraid you'll only have six months to live.

240
00:14:21,050 --> 00:14:22,530
It's fine.

241
00:14:22,970 --> 00:14:24,130
When she was in trouble,

242
00:14:24,130 --> 00:14:26,460
I couldn't just stand by and watch her die.

243
00:14:26,820 --> 00:14:28,680
Is it because you couldn't stand by and watch her die

244
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:31,610
or you still have feelings for Ms. Qiao?

245
00:14:33,230 --> 00:14:35,120
Old Monk, don't talk nonsense.

246
00:14:35,390 --> 00:14:36,470
Mian is the only one

247
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:38,770
who can offer me clues to find the corpse of my senior.

248
00:14:38,770 --> 00:14:40,230
Of course I care about her.

249
00:14:41,340 --> 00:14:42,930
People go to heaven when they die.

250
00:14:42,930 --> 00:14:45,060
Why do you insist

251
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:47,370
on finding the corpse of Mr. Shan?

252
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:48,790
Why don't you come back?

253
00:14:52,340 --> 00:14:53,710
You've met Yun Biqiu.

254
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:57,330
I know you don't mind

255
00:14:57,420 --> 00:14:59,700
that he was bewitched by Jiao Liqiao

256
00:15:00,180 --> 00:15:02,180
and poisoned you with Bicha Poison.

257
00:15:03,230 --> 00:15:04,260
Bicha Poison?

258
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:08,550
I won.

259
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:14,270
Ten years ago, Di Feisheng wanted to battle with you.

260
00:15:15,270 --> 00:15:16,850
But he didn't expect

261
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,510
the one he won in the end

262
00:15:19,020 --> 00:15:21,220
was poisoned with a deadly poison.

263
00:15:22,530 --> 00:15:23,050
Since

264
00:15:23,050 --> 00:15:25,850
you don't mind that he helped Di Feisheng harm you,

265
00:15:26,940 --> 00:15:28,270
why don't you come back?

266
00:15:28,540 --> 00:15:31,070
If you don't want to say it, I'll say it for you.

267
00:15:31,750 --> 00:15:34,340
You always think it was because you acted willfully

268
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:35,940
and declared war on the Jinyuan Alliance

269
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:37,020
that

270
00:15:37,040 --> 00:15:40,250
the 58 heroes of the Sigu Sect died tragically

271
00:15:40,270 --> 00:15:42,640
and that the Sigu Sect split.

272
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:47,350
It's not that you can't forgive others.

273
00:15:48,570 --> 00:15:50,900
It's that you refuse to forgive yourself.

274
00:15:51,350 --> 00:15:52,080
Are you done?

275
00:15:52,820 --> 00:15:54,880
If you're done, let me say something.

276
00:15:55,830 --> 00:15:56,510
Old Monk.

277
00:15:57,030 --> 00:15:59,490
When did you become an old storyteller monk?

278
00:16:00,160 --> 00:16:01,000
I just think

279
00:16:01,030 --> 00:16:03,510
being Li Xiangyi is too tiring.

280
00:16:04,020 --> 00:16:05,680
Isn't it good to be Li Lianhua?

281
00:16:05,860 --> 00:16:07,190
I can drink tea with you.

282
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:08,930
Stop it.

283
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:10,970
It's time for you

284
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:13,510
to give lessons to the little monks.

285
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:14,990
Why are you still sitting here?

286
00:16:14,990 --> 00:16:17,990
Otherwise, those little monks will raise the roof again.

287
00:16:17,990 --> 00:16:18,910
Hurry up and go.

288
00:16:39,760 --> 00:16:40,510
Li Xiangyi!

289
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:42,020
Li Xiangyi.

290
00:16:43,040 --> 00:16:44,100
What are you doing?

291
00:16:44,150 --> 00:16:44,620
Ten years ago,

292
00:16:44,620 --> 00:16:46,540
you lost to me because you were poisoned.

293
00:16:46,540 --> 00:16:47,400
Let me tell you.

294
00:16:47,700 --> 00:16:50,280
Eavesdropping is not a good habit.

295
00:16:54,050 --> 00:16:55,110
What are you doing?

296
00:16:55,210 --> 00:16:57,540
In the battle at the East Sea ten years ago,

297
00:16:57,770 --> 00:16:59,440
I thought I was the world number one

298
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:01,170
because I won a narrow victory.

299
00:17:01,470 --> 00:17:04,630
Today I heard that I won in an unfair way.

300
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:07,570
You mean you didn't know anything about this?

301
00:17:09,260 --> 00:17:10,460
Are you insulting me?

302
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:14,800
I see.

303
00:17:15,970 --> 00:17:16,569
Forget it.

304
00:17:16,990 --> 00:17:18,319
Let bygones be bygones.

305
00:17:18,589 --> 00:17:19,940
It doesn't matter who won or lost.

306
00:17:19,940 --> 00:17:20,599
It matters.

307
00:17:21,900 --> 00:17:23,910
I treated you as a worthy opponent.

308
00:17:25,030 --> 00:17:26,680
You made me a joke.

309
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,650
Director Di.

310
00:17:30,130 --> 00:17:31,480
It's been so long.

311
00:17:31,579 --> 00:17:34,480
Just pretend that you didn't hear it, okay?

312
00:17:35,020 --> 00:17:35,660
No.

313
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:38,079
I want to compete with you again.

314
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:40,480
Let's compete in a fair way.

315
00:17:40,870 --> 00:17:43,670
The problem is that I can't compete with you again.

316
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:45,130
You know that.

317
00:17:46,370 --> 00:17:48,220
Since you've eavesdropped.

318
00:17:49,340 --> 00:17:49,840
Now,

319
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:52,170
the poison has entered my bone marrow.

320
00:17:52,170 --> 00:17:54,140
I only have ten percent of my inner power.

321
00:17:54,140 --> 00:17:56,800
Why don't you take a look at the new ranking list?

322
00:17:57,080 --> 00:17:59,640
I heard Buddhist San Sheng is quite awesome.

323
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:01,560
Go and compete with them.

324
00:18:01,650 --> 00:18:04,570
I have only one opponent in my life.

325
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:06,430
That is Li Xiangyi.

326
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:09,260
I only have one wish in my life.

327
00:18:09,780 --> 00:18:10,840
That is to beat him.

328
00:18:10,860 --> 00:18:11,790
I'm sorry.

329
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:13,080
I can't help you.

330
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:14,600
Now,

331
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:16,420
you're the world number one.

332
00:18:20,830 --> 00:18:22,460
I don't need you to let me win.

333
00:18:23,130 --> 00:18:24,460
It's just Bicha Poison.

334
00:18:24,940 --> 00:18:26,400
I'll find a way to cure you.

335
00:18:27,860 --> 00:18:29,030
I heard the poison

336
00:18:29,500 --> 00:18:31,230
was created by Medicine Demon.

337
00:18:31,400 --> 00:18:33,400
No one can detoxify it in this world.

338
00:18:33,660 --> 00:18:36,860
Besides, Bhante Wuliao has excellent medical skills.

339
00:18:37,130 --> 00:18:39,560
He hasn't cured me during these ten years.

340
00:18:39,820 --> 00:18:42,380
It doesn't mean I can't cure you.

341
00:18:43,020 --> 00:18:44,820
Tell me the Mantra of Inner Body Cleansing.

342
00:18:44,820 --> 00:18:46,210
I'll find a way to save you.

343
00:18:46,210 --> 00:18:47,540
Do you think I'm stupid?

344
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:49,830
The Mantra of Inner Body Cleansing.

345
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:51,120
It's easy.

346
00:18:51,910 --> 00:18:54,240
If you help me find the corpse of my senior,

347
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:55,440
I'll tell it to you.

348
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:57,860
Otherwise, there will be nothing to be discussed.

349
00:18:57,860 --> 00:19:01,260
The corpse of your senior, Shan Gudao,

350
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:03,590
has long become soil.

351
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:05,400
Even if it has become soil,

352
00:19:06,220 --> 00:19:07,820
according to our agreement,

353
00:19:08,610 --> 00:19:09,410
if you have it,

354
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:11,210
I'll swap with you.

355
00:19:11,610 --> 00:19:14,610
If you don't have it, I don't have what you want either.

356
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:19,010
Are you really not afraid of death?

357
00:19:19,780 --> 00:19:22,130
I already died ten years ago.

358
00:19:22,260 --> 00:19:23,860
Then I'll kill Qiao Wanmian.

359
00:19:23,900 --> 00:19:24,980
Bullying the weak

360
00:19:25,150 --> 00:19:26,390
is more unjust, isn't it?

361
00:19:26,390 --> 00:19:27,800
Then I'll wipe out the Baichuan Court.

362
00:19:27,800 --> 00:19:31,330
Even if you wipe out the whole world, it has nothing to do with me.

363
00:19:32,170 --> 00:19:33,370
Let go of him!

364
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:35,020
Don't you know he's in poor health?

365
00:19:35,020 --> 00:19:36,260
He even doesn't care about his life.

366
00:19:36,260 --> 00:19:37,190
What do you care about?

367
00:19:37,190 --> 00:19:38,250
Listen carefully.

368
00:19:38,590 --> 00:19:40,150
I don't care what happened between you two.

369
00:19:40,150 --> 00:19:41,740
A gentleman uses words but not his fists.

370
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:44,140
I won't go easy on you if you keep doing this.

371
00:19:46,860 --> 00:19:49,460
I don't believe you don't care about anything.

372
00:19:56,130 --> 00:19:57,340
Jiao Liqiao.

373
00:20:05,450 --> 00:20:06,170
Hey,

374
00:20:06,740 --> 00:20:08,670
what happened between you and Fei?

375
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:10,880
There's a misunderstanding.

376
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:11,370
Go on.

377
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:12,750
Keep making it up.

378
00:20:13,180 --> 00:20:14,860
I'd like to see what kind of misunderstanding

379
00:20:14,860 --> 00:20:17,060
caused him to almost choke you to death.

380
00:20:17,580 --> 00:20:18,820
If you keep talking,

381
00:20:19,350 --> 00:20:20,650
I'll feel dizzy.

382
00:20:24,770 --> 00:20:25,360
Enough.

383
00:20:26,040 --> 00:20:27,370
I just want to remind you

384
00:20:27,550 --> 00:20:29,150
although Fei is not skilled in martial arts,

385
00:20:29,150 --> 00:20:30,670
he's ruthless when he fights.

386
00:20:30,670 --> 00:20:32,980
You can't let this kind of person stay by your side.

387
00:20:32,980 --> 00:20:34,910
Maybe one day when I'm not with you,

388
00:20:34,980 --> 00:20:36,380
he'll choke you to death.

389
00:20:37,250 --> 00:20:38,690
Pour me some water.

390
00:20:39,210 --> 00:20:40,340
My hands feel weak.

391
00:20:44,060 --> 00:20:44,920
Think about it.

392
00:20:45,190 --> 00:20:46,280
Fei

393
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:47,460
is indeed weired,

394
00:20:47,980 --> 00:20:48,650
but

395
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,640
he doesn't want me to die either.

396
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:51,750
As you saw before,

397
00:20:51,900 --> 00:20:54,010
he's crazy and flaky.

398
00:20:54,120 --> 00:20:55,930
He's a bit out of his mind.

399
00:20:56,620 --> 00:20:58,860
Besides, I have you.

400
00:21:00,670 --> 00:21:01,270
By the way,

401
00:21:01,700 --> 00:21:04,470
I asked you to investigate Cailian Manor in the Baichuan Court yesterday.

402
00:21:04,470 --> 00:21:05,730
Did you find anything?

403
00:21:05,860 --> 00:21:06,710
You don't tell me

404
00:21:06,710 --> 00:21:08,310
what you're thinking about.

405
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:10,230
But you ask me to do many things.

406
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:15,230
There really were murder cases in Cailian Manor.

407
00:21:20,120 --> 00:21:22,600
[Baichuan Court's Casebook]

408
00:21:20,120 --> 00:21:22,600
[Wedding Dress Murder Cases in Cailian Manor]

409
00:21:22,900 --> 00:21:24,500
Wedding Dress Murder Cases.

410
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:28,680
Three wedding ceremonies have been held in Cailian Manor during these ten years.

411
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:29,600
[Cailian Manor]

412
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,370
Three brides died.

413
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:31,950
Strangely,

414
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:34,790
it happened at intervals of a few years.

415
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:36,520
But when the three brides died,

416
00:21:36,530 --> 00:21:38,390
they wore the same wedding dress.

417
00:21:39,460 --> 00:21:41,730
It's said that the source of the wedding dress is unknown.

418
00:21:41,730 --> 00:21:43,160
There's resentment on it.

419
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:45,790
Everyone who wears it will suffer misfortune.

420
00:21:49,620 --> 00:21:51,120
It's horrible.

421
00:21:51,820 --> 00:21:53,080
After all these years,

422
00:21:54,410 --> 00:21:56,040
haven't they found any clues to the identities

423
00:21:56,040 --> 00:21:58,040
of the murderers of the three cases?

424
00:21:59,090 --> 00:22:01,140
They were all considered as accidents.

425
00:22:01,140 --> 00:22:01,780
Maybe

426
00:22:02,510 --> 00:22:04,860
they were really caused by the wedding dress.

427
00:22:04,860 --> 00:22:05,970
I saw it just now.

428
00:22:07,380 --> 00:22:10,940
The last time this wedding dress killed someone

429
00:22:11,080 --> 00:22:12,080
was a few days ago.

430
00:22:12,700 --> 00:22:13,600
The person who died

431
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:17,060
was the new bride of Guo Huo, the young master of Cailian Manor.

432
00:22:18,270 --> 00:22:19,440
I haven't asked you yet.

433
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:20,540
Why did you suddenly ask me to investigate

434
00:22:20,540 --> 00:22:22,270
the cases about Cailian Manor?

435
00:22:22,700 --> 00:22:24,100
I'm looking for a person.

436
00:22:25,570 --> 00:22:26,870
His name is Shi Hun.

437
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:29,050
As long as I find him,

438
00:22:29,210 --> 00:22:31,660
I can find the whereabouts of my other friend.

439
00:22:31,660 --> 00:22:32,610
The last time he was heard from

440
00:22:32,610 --> 00:22:34,700
was ten years ago in Cailian Manor.

441
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:36,720
It was also ten years ago?

442
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:38,330
Your friend appeared

443
00:22:38,350 --> 00:22:39,670
in Cailian Manor ten years ago.

444
00:22:39,670 --> 00:22:41,220
The first murder in Cailian Manor

445
00:22:41,220 --> 00:22:42,560
also happened ten years ago.

446
00:22:42,560 --> 00:22:43,690
What a coincidence!

447
00:22:44,150 --> 00:22:45,550
Is there any connection?

448
00:22:45,550 --> 00:22:46,810
Your analysis is good.

449
00:22:48,490 --> 00:22:50,100
There's a very high possibility.

450
00:22:50,100 --> 00:22:51,900
Three murders happened in a row.

451
00:22:52,190 --> 00:22:53,120
Detective Fang.

452
00:22:53,540 --> 00:22:55,930
You have to go to Cailian Manor.

453
00:22:57,020 --> 00:22:57,760
Cut it out.

454
00:22:58,860 --> 00:23:01,260
You just want me to help you look for people.

455
00:23:01,540 --> 00:23:02,800
I don't have time for that.

456
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:04,800
I finally have clues to the whereabouts of Di Feisheng.

457
00:23:04,800 --> 00:23:05,800
I must find him.

458
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:07,270
Fine.

459
00:23:07,460 --> 00:23:08,820
When I find Shi Hun,

460
00:23:09,020 --> 00:23:11,620
I'll help you ask him about the whereabouts of Di Feisheng.

461
00:23:11,620 --> 00:23:12,550
What do you mean?

462
00:23:12,780 --> 00:23:15,510
Because Shi Hun belongs to the Jinyuan Alliance.

463
00:23:15,770 --> 00:23:16,800
You did it on purpose, didn't you?

464
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:17,930
Are you going or not?

465
00:23:19,620 --> 00:23:20,130
No.

466
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:24,840
By the way,

467
00:23:25,970 --> 00:23:26,950
I bought some expensive medicine

468
00:23:26,950 --> 00:23:28,880
such as Cordyceps and tiger bones.

469
00:23:28,910 --> 00:23:30,840
Take it. It's good for your health.

470
00:23:31,450 --> 00:23:31,970
Wait.

471
00:23:36,630 --> 00:23:37,430
Fang Duobing.

472
00:23:37,750 --> 00:23:39,270
You're penniless.

473
00:23:39,600 --> 00:23:41,730
Where did you get the money to buy this?

474
00:23:43,550 --> 00:23:44,210
It's yours.

475
00:23:45,650 --> 00:23:46,390
Mine?

476
00:23:48,140 --> 00:23:49,340
Where did you find it?

477
00:23:49,820 --> 00:23:51,990
Your drawers, cabinets, and bedsides.

478
00:23:51,990 --> 00:23:52,370
Also,

479
00:23:52,730 --> 00:23:54,510
there was some money hidden under your rice jar.

480
00:23:54,510 --> 00:23:57,440
Aren't these the places where you hide your nest egg?

481
00:24:02,060 --> 00:24:02,560
Good.

482
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:03,920
Very good.

483
00:24:05,260 --> 00:24:06,190
How can we go now?

484
00:24:06,920 --> 00:24:08,320
There's not a penny left.

485
00:24:08,350 --> 00:24:09,080
How can we go?

486
00:24:09,260 --> 00:24:09,710
No.

487
00:24:10,670 --> 00:24:11,770
That's all you hid?

488
00:24:12,860 --> 00:24:13,780
Where else could I hide?

489
00:24:13,780 --> 00:24:14,130
I...

490
00:24:20,530 --> 00:24:24,090
[Cailian Manor]

491
00:24:25,980 --> 00:24:29,050
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

492
00:24:35,830 --> 00:24:36,360
Go ahead.

493
00:24:39,700 --> 00:24:41,630
Do you still need travel expenses?

494
00:24:44,530 --> 00:24:45,790
Ladies and gentlemen.

495
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:46,550
Come here.

496
00:24:46,740 --> 00:24:48,070
Here are vegetables for sale!

497
00:24:48,070 --> 00:24:49,210
Fresh vegetables!

498
00:24:49,890 --> 00:24:51,150
-Come and have a look.
-The vegetables are good.

499
00:24:51,150 --> 00:24:51,730
The vegetables are good.

500
00:24:51,730 --> 00:24:52,070
Yes.

501
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:53,500
They're very fresh.

502
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:54,670
Listen to me.

503
00:24:55,360 --> 00:24:56,110
These vegetables

504
00:24:56,110 --> 00:24:57,440
were just dug out of the ground.

505
00:24:57,440 --> 00:24:58,410
They're very fresh.

506
00:24:58,410 --> 00:24:59,270
Let me tell you.

507
00:24:59,350 --> 00:25:00,330
Most importantly,

508
00:25:00,330 --> 00:25:01,420
if you buy these vegetables,

509
00:25:01,420 --> 00:25:02,920
this young man will deliver them to your houses.

510
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:03,830
-Deliver them?
-Really?

511
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:04,230
You...

512
00:25:04,710 --> 00:25:05,420
So nice.

513
00:25:05,460 --> 00:25:06,360
Give it to me.

514
00:25:06,380 --> 00:25:06,930
Take your time.

515
00:25:06,930 --> 00:25:08,490
Take your time.

516
00:25:09,180 --> 00:25:09,910
Three taels.

517
00:25:10,190 --> 00:25:10,870
Perfect.

518
00:25:11,220 --> 00:25:12,100
Take your time.

519
00:25:13,390 --> 00:25:14,830
Li Lianhua, why did you leave?

520
00:25:14,830 --> 00:25:16,260
How much is half a kilo of vegetables?

521
00:25:16,260 --> 00:25:17,790
Why did you leave me behind?

522
00:25:18,270 --> 00:25:20,130
Everyone has a chance to buy them.

523
00:25:21,120 --> 00:25:22,230
My Lord.

524
00:25:23,380 --> 00:25:25,780
I want to know how to detoxify Bicha Poison.

525
00:25:26,100 --> 00:25:26,460
Yes.

526
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:27,560
Also,

527
00:25:28,810 --> 00:25:30,520
go and fish for information about the Tianji Hall's young master,

528
00:25:30,520 --> 00:25:31,430
Fang Duobing.

529
00:25:31,610 --> 00:25:32,940
It might be useful to me.

530
00:25:32,970 --> 00:25:35,770
Don't let Jiao Liqiao's people know these things.

531
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:37,030
I'll do it right away.

532
00:25:44,900 --> 00:25:45,830
Why are you here?

533
00:25:47,980 --> 00:25:49,180
Who was that just now?

534
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,070
Stop!

535
00:25:52,550 --> 00:25:53,810
Li Lianhua is not here.

536
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:55,730
I have something to ask you.

537
00:25:56,980 --> 00:25:58,410
Why did you hit him today?

538
00:26:01,580 --> 00:26:02,440
Say something.

539
00:26:02,730 --> 00:26:04,520
I know you are not Iron Head Slave.

540
00:26:04,520 --> 00:26:05,520
So I want to ask you

541
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,630
why you approached us.

542
00:26:08,010 --> 00:26:10,210
What makes you think you have something

543
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:11,710
that is worthy of approach?

544
00:26:11,710 --> 00:26:12,110
You...

545
00:26:14,140 --> 00:26:15,670
You are here for Li Lianhua.

546
00:26:17,170 --> 00:26:18,900
Do you think I came here for you?

547
00:26:21,230 --> 00:26:21,830
Forget it.

548
00:26:22,690 --> 00:26:23,620
I don't argue with people

549
00:26:23,620 --> 00:26:25,150
who're not good at martial arts.

550
00:26:25,150 --> 00:26:26,610
I don't want to talk to you.

551
00:26:38,750 --> 00:26:39,810
I'm a man of my word.

552
00:26:40,330 --> 00:26:42,190
I'll let you battle with me again.

553
00:26:44,700 --> 00:26:47,180
The last place Shi Hun appeared is Cailian Manor.

554
00:26:47,180 --> 00:26:48,400
I'll go there with you.

555
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:50,460
When you find the corpse of Shan Gudao,

556
00:26:50,460 --> 00:26:51,990
don't forget your promise.

557
00:26:55,900 --> 00:26:56,940
He's so stubborn.

558
00:27:08,530 --> 00:27:09,190
Li Lianhua.

559
00:27:10,390 --> 00:27:11,720
Let me tell you a secret.

560
00:27:12,700 --> 00:27:13,410
Fei

561
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:15,960
met someone secretly yesterday.

562
00:27:16,240 --> 00:27:17,840
I also followed that person.

563
00:27:17,940 --> 00:27:20,070
Unfortunately, that person ran away.

