00:39:07,610 --> 00:39:08,900
This is the best place to admire the lotuses.

842
00:39:08,900 --> 00:39:09,500
Thank you.

843
00:39:18,740 --> 00:39:20,270
This is indeed a good place.

844
00:39:20,420 --> 00:39:21,550
It's such a big pond.

845
00:39:21,580 --> 00:39:23,450
We might be able to even catch fishes here.

846
00:39:23,450 --> 00:39:25,250
It's useless for you to be anxious.

847
00:39:25,250 --> 00:39:27,440
What if Master Guo hides something deliberately?

848
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:29,440
If you ask him now, you'll alert him.

849
00:39:29,580 --> 00:39:30,380
Why don't you

850
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:32,010
investigate the case about Cailian Manor

851
00:39:32,010 --> 00:39:33,910
and find out what happened ten years ago?

852
00:39:33,910 --> 00:39:35,570
Maybe there will be new clues.

853
00:39:36,810 --> 00:39:39,610
You still want me to help you investigate the case.

854
00:39:40,270 --> 00:39:40,870
It's easy.

855
00:39:41,330 --> 00:39:43,290
I'll go and torture Guo Qian.

856
00:39:44,060 --> 00:39:44,580
Fei.

857
00:39:44,780 --> 00:39:45,650
Don't act recklessly.

858
00:39:45,650 --> 00:39:46,520
Fang Duobing, don't chase him.

859
00:39:46,520 --> 00:39:47,120
Let him go.

860
00:39:48,050 --> 00:39:49,340
He has no experience in investigating cases.

861
00:39:49,340 --> 00:39:50,390
He's also violent.

862
00:39:50,390 --> 00:39:51,740
If he gets angry and hits others,

863
00:39:51,740 --> 00:39:52,160
then...

864
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:53,320
He won't. Don't worry.

865
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:54,360
He's an adult.

866
00:39:57,380 --> 00:39:58,050
Li Lianhua.

867
00:39:58,690 --> 00:40:00,460
I'm becoming more and more curious.

868
00:40:00,460 --> 00:40:01,920
Do you trust him that much?

869
00:40:02,480 --> 00:40:03,190
Trust?

870
00:40:05,640 --> 00:40:07,350
The deceased hasn't been buried yet.

871
00:40:07,350 --> 00:40:09,140
Why don't we go to the mourning hall and burn incense sticks for her?

872
00:40:09,140 --> 00:40:09,490
Let's go.

873
00:40:09,490 --> 00:40:09,890
You...

874
00:40:16,020 --> 00:40:17,330
The coffin should be kept here for seven days.

875
00:40:17,330 --> 00:40:19,260
Only three days passed, but no one is here now.

876
00:40:19,260 --> 00:40:21,450
People of Cailian Manor really don't care about

877
00:40:21,450 --> 00:40:23,180
this young madam who just died.

878
00:40:29,380 --> 00:40:29,900
Look.

879
00:40:30,160 --> 00:40:30,980
Abdominal distension.

880
00:40:30,980 --> 00:40:32,040
There's water inside.

881
00:40:32,040 --> 00:40:33,700
It does look like she drowned.

882
00:40:33,790 --> 00:40:34,920
The body is swollen.

883
00:40:35,110 --> 00:40:36,440
The spots are light red.

884
00:40:36,620 --> 00:40:38,960
It does look like the spots appeared slowly

885
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:41,080
because the body was soaked before.

886
00:40:42,140 --> 00:40:44,220
She has a lot of bruises on her neck.

887
00:40:48,850 --> 00:40:49,920
What are you doing?

888
00:40:51,120 --> 00:40:52,120
Young Master Guo.

889
00:40:52,170 --> 00:40:53,930
There's still something fishy about your wife's death.

890
00:40:53,930 --> 00:40:55,260
We want to check it again

891
00:40:55,390 --> 00:40:57,230
to bring justice to the deceased.

892
00:40:57,230 --> 00:40:59,220
What should be checked has already been checked.

893
00:40:59,220 --> 00:41:00,270
She has already passed away.

894
00:41:00,270 --> 00:41:02,270
Please don't disturb the deceased.

895
00:41:02,940 --> 00:41:03,780
Young Master Guo.

896
00:41:03,780 --> 00:41:04,660
To be honest,

897
00:41:05,110 --> 00:41:07,120
your wife appeared in my dream a few days ago.

898
00:41:07,120 --> 00:41:08,150
She cried and expressed her grievances.

899
00:41:08,150 --> 00:41:09,290
She said she couldn't rest in peace.

900
00:41:09,290 --> 00:41:11,020
That's why we came to Cailian Manor.

901
00:41:11,020 --> 00:41:12,550
She appeared in your dream?

902
00:41:13,550 --> 00:41:15,410
This is the master of Lotus Tower.

903
00:41:15,560 --> 00:41:17,220
People call him Physician Li.

904
00:41:17,390 --> 00:41:18,340
He's psychic.

905
00:41:18,730 --> 00:41:20,260
His dreams are believable.

906
00:41:21,310 --> 00:41:22,230
Even so,

907
00:41:22,670 --> 00:41:24,270
I should tell my father first

908
00:41:24,520 --> 00:41:26,070
and get his permission.

909
00:41:26,290 --> 00:41:28,220
You seem to be afraid of Master Guo.

910
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:30,890
It's right and proper that children obey their fathers' orders.

911
00:41:30,890 --> 00:41:31,890
Young Master Guo.

912
00:41:32,270 --> 00:41:33,920
Now that the coffin has been opened,

913
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:35,580
she's already been offended.

914
00:41:35,750 --> 00:41:37,700
I'll apologize to Master Guo later.

915
00:41:37,700 --> 00:41:38,960
If he really blames us,

916
00:41:39,230 --> 00:41:41,030
I'll take full responsibility.

917
00:41:44,080 --> 00:41:46,230
This body didn't just have superficial injuries.

918
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:48,070
Her carpal bones were fractured.

919
00:41:48,070 --> 00:41:50,670
Her cervical spine was also severely damaged.

920
00:41:51,350 --> 00:41:52,920
We never hit her.

921
00:41:53,220 --> 00:41:55,340
The people from the government have already investigated before.

922
00:41:55,340 --> 00:41:57,500
They said the bride fell into the water by accident

923
00:41:57,500 --> 00:41:59,750
and that the injuries were caused when she struggled.

924
00:41:59,750 --> 00:42:01,860
It doesn't seem like she was beaten up.

925
00:42:01,860 --> 00:42:02,860
Young Master Guo.

926
00:42:03,300 --> 00:42:05,700
Did anything happen before the bride died?

927
00:42:07,590 --> 00:42:09,230
There was nothing special.

928
00:42:10,930 --> 00:42:12,650
After she had dinner that night,

929
00:42:12,650 --> 00:42:14,310
Su went back to our room alone.

930
00:42:14,310 --> 00:42:17,240
She said she wanted to try on the wedding dress again.

931
00:42:25,700 --> 00:42:27,070
No one knows what happened

932
00:42:27,070 --> 00:42:28,710
after the bride went back to the room?

